      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Capital A 的 Teleport 目标是在航空公司分拆后实现快速增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/capital-a-s-teleport-targets-rapid-growth-after-airline-spinoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席执行官 Pete Chareonwongsak 表示，Capital A Bhd. 的物流部门 Teleport 不会受到该集团即将剥离的航空资产的阻碍，并怀有自己的 IPO 雄心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/capital-a-s-teleport-targets-rapid-growth-after-airline-spinoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 03:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>财团收购后，ESR 实现 2020 年以来最大增幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/esr-jumps-most-since-2020-after-starwood-consortium-takeover-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ESR Group Ltd. 收到投资者财团的非约束性收购提议后，该公司股价创下四年多以来的最大涨幅，证实了彭博新闻社早些时候的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/esr-jumps-most-since-2020-after-starwood-consortium-takeover-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 02:02:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行政策押注推动日本债券收益率攀升至十年高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/japan-20-year-yield-hits-highest-since-2013-on-boj-policy-bets-lw5o11fi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本主权债券收益率飙升至十多年来的最高水平，有迹象表明日本央行准备减少债务购买，以缓解日元疲软的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/japan-20-year-yield-hits-highest-since-2013-on-boj-policy-bets-lw5o11fi</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 00:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>野村证券寻求双倍利润，让批发部门付出代价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/nomura-seeks-to-double-profit-by-2030-in-latest-growth-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村控股公司(Nomura Holdings Inc.)公布了到本世纪末将利润几乎翻倍的计划，部分方法是让其主要批发部门为自己的业务提供资金，并将资源转移到其想要增长的领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/nomura-seeks-to-double-profit-by-2030-in-latest-growth-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 00:06:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
