      <title>交易员关注欧佩克报告和通胀数据，油价稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧佩克市场前景公布之前，油价保持上涨，交易员正在寻找供应限制是否会延长的迹象，以及将影响货币政策预期的美国通胀数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 23:29:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国科技股跑赢大盘，日本国债收益率上升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着更广泛的区域指数下跌，中国科技股在行业领头羊公布财报之前上涨。日本国债收益率攀升至十多年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 22:27:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国废旧食用油泛滥引发美国提高关税的呼声</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/flood-of-chinese-used-cooking-oil-spurs-call-to-boost-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统乔·拜登准备对中国征收新一波关税之际，美国一个大豆贸易组织正在推动对中国废食用油征收更高的关税，该组织称这会削弱美国用于生物燃料的农作物的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/flood-of-chinese-used-cooking-oil-spurs-call-to-boost-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 21:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
